NB. General file move/copy utilities
NB. file move (Fmove 'infile';'outfile')  NB. rank 1 boxed
Fmove=:(2!:0@('/bin/mv '&,)@;@:(,&' '@('"'&([ , [ ,~ ]))&.>))"1

NB. file copy (Fcopy 'infile';'outfile')  NB. rank 1 boxed
Fcopy=:(2!:0@('/bin/cp '&,)@;@:(,&' '@('"'&([ , [ ,~ ]))&.>))"1
